<span id="freeTextContainer16388879952263614534">It&apos;s the story of an Irish family that is as fractured as it could possibly be, brought reluctantly together by the tragedy of a son/brother dying of Aids. Heartbreaking and devastating, and it will leave you drained at the end.<br/><br/>4.5 stars for what may be Toibin&apos;s best novel.</span>
  <span id="freeText16388879952263614534" style="display:none">It's the story of an Irish family that is as fractured as it could possibly be, brought reluctantly together by the tragedy of a son/brother dying of Aids. Heartbreaking and devastating, and it will leave you drained at the end.<br /><br />4.5 stars for what may be Toibin's best novel.</span>
